@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam nodeStyle rectangle

node "Host PC (x86_64 + NVIDIA GPU)" as HOST {
  frame "CLI / Makefile" {
    [make data] as MAKE_DATA
    [yopo train] as YOPO_TRAIN_LOCAL
    [yopo deploy run] as YOPO_DEPLOY
    [yopo trt] as YOPO_TRT
  }

  frame "Docker Engine" {
    component "yopo-data-gen:latest\n(CUDA 单机)" as DG_CONT
    component "yopo-train:latest\n(uv + CUDA + 数据生成)" as T_CONT
  }

  file "./dataset/" as DSET_LOCAL
  file "./YOPO/saved/" as SAVED_LOCAL
  file "./deploy.yaml" as DEPLOY_YAML
}

node "远程训练服务器\n(user@10.0.0.5)" as REMOTE {
  folder "/data/yopo/dataset" as DSET_REMOTE
  folder "/data/yopo/saved" as SAVED_REMOTE
  folder "/data/yopo/configs" as CFG_REMOTE

  component "yopo-train:latest\n(后台容器)" as T_CONT_REMOTE
}

node "Jetson Orin NX" as ORIN {
  frame "ROS 控制器" {
    [network_control_node] as ORIN_CTRL
    [HGDO] as HGDO2
  }
  [MAVROS (PX4)] as PX4
}

node "RK3566\n(机载协处理器，实验性)" as RK {
  [sensor_simulator (CPU)] as RK_SIM
  [dataset_generator] as RK_DGEN
}

HOST --> REMOTE : SSH / SCP (部署管线)
HOST --> DG_CONT : docker build + run
HOST --> T_CONT : docker build + run (本地训练)
T_CONT_REMOTE --> DSET_REMOTE : /app/dataset/data
T_CONT_REMOTE --> SAVED_REMOTE : /app/YOPO/saved
T_CONT_REMOTE --> CFG_REMOTE : /app/configs
ORIN_CTRL --> PX4 : mavros (AttitudeTarget)
ORIN_CTRL --> RK_SIM : ROS topics (仿真模式)

@enduml
```

**Source anchors:**
- `deploy.yaml` — Remote target (user@10.0.0.5), volume paths, image spec
- `YOPO/schema.py` — RemoteTarget, DockerImageSpec, DeployConfig
- `Makefile` — `make data` 管线用于数据生成 Docker
- `YOPO/cli.py` — cmd_deploy_run (4 阶段管线), cmd_data_gen, cmd_docker_build, cmd_trt
- `docker/data-gen/Dockerfile` — CUDA 12.4.1, nvidia/cuda 基础镜像
- `docker/train/Dockerfile` — 多阶段：数据生成构建器 + uv 训练环境
- `docker/train/entrypoint.sh` — 自动数据集生成，`uv run yopo "$@"`
- `Controller/src/so3_control/launch/controller_network.launch` — 将 topic 重新映射到 /vins_estimator/imu_propagate (Orin VIO)
